Here's Laravel documentation and Laravel Packages to be used at this task

Laravel documentation https://laravel.com/docs/5.4 (read Setup, The Basics)
For localization use https://github.com/mcamara/laravel-localization
For translation use https://github.com/dimsav/laravel-translatable

Task Details

There’s Admin Area which will have: (find HTML template here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B70kKr4PaNRzRHJWdG9lTVhtUGc/view?usp=sharing)
Login Page
Dashboard have 3 menus

Users (CURD)
First Name
Last Name
E-mail
Password

Categories (CURD)
Slug
English Name
Arabic Name

Posts (CURD)
Category
English Title
Arabic Title
Image
English Description
Arabic Description

Note that categories and posts modules are translatable (so don’t forget to use Translation packages referenced above).

Frontend: (there’s no design so feel free whatever you want even HTML without any styling)
List of categories
When you click on any category this will redirect you to this category page which list all posts under this category (use pagination: 10 posts by page)
Post will include Title and just 10 words from description and read more button.
when you click on read more button for any post listed at category page this will redirect to single post page which include chosen Post Title, Image, Description.

Note that Frontend in 2 languages (English  and Arabic) so make sure that you display content in a proper language. (Use localization package referenced above to manage languages and translation package referenced above to display content in a proper language).
